PrecisAuthority for the Canada Ports Corporation to enter into an Agreement with The New Brunswick Electric Power Commission which, in summary, provides for an exchange of titles to a number of pieces of land situate at the Port of Belledune and for the construction of coal-handling docks and other ancillary works as well as for the granting of new leases and easements to Shell Canada Products Limited and to Brunswick Mining and Smelting Corporation Limited, whose facilities were or will be relocated.
